11:30.063 --> 11:31.607
I know you don't like it.

11:33.109 --> 11:36.029
Hello. Welcome to day two.

11:36.321 --> 11:38.533
The trail is along here.

11:38.783 --> 11:41.245
It should be pretty obvious.

11:42.747 --> 11:44.624
You guys heard of
the Blair witch?

11:44.916 --> 11:47.670
I heard the myth. I don't
really believe much in it.

11:47.962 --> 11:48.796
The myth?

11:48.921 --> 11:50.632
That's all I think it is.

11:50.841 --> 11:51.925
What'd you say, sir?

11:52.092 --> 11:54.470
- I said damn fool kids never learn.
- Shut up.

11:54.762 --> 11:56.223
Damn fool kids never learn?

11:56.389 --> 11:57.140
That's what I said.

11:57.307 --> 11:58.642
Why do you say that?

11:58.851 --> 12:01.146
First of all, can I
have your permission...

12:01.354 --> 12:04.108
...to use your image on a
video documentary?

12:04.525 --> 12:06.486
I don't care about that, but...

12:06.778 --> 12:08.489
