12:41.031 --> 12:43.243
- She was babbling something...
- Her story.

12:43.451 --> 12:45.662
Babbling something about...

12:45.913 --> 12:48.458
...an old woman whose feet
never touched the ground.

12:50.335 --> 12:54.007
I saw... just by that
tree up the creek...

12:55.050 --> 12:56.510
...about a hundred yards,

12:57.052 --> 13:00.974
I saw a white misty thing.
Can't tell you what it was.

13:01.183 --> 13:04.354
Like grey vapor rising
out of the trees.

13:04.562 --> 13:05.981
Right out of the water.

13:06.189 --> 13:07.107
Right out of the water?

13:07.316 --> 13:09.694
Up the side of the trees,
Then it disappeared.

13:09.944 --> 13:11.363
You're full of it.

13:11.530 --> 13:13.657
I'm not. And I wasn't
drinking that day, either.

13:13.950 --> 13:14.701
Sure you weren't.

13:14.909 --> 13:16.870
How is that related to the
story of Coffin Rock?

13:17.079 --> 13:19.624
It all ties in to the
story of Coffin Rock.

13:19.791 --> 13:20.458
How's that?

13:21.877 --> 13:24.964
Anybody round here...

13:25.173 --> 13:28.177
...knows that the old woman has
haunted this area for years.

13:28.427 --> 13:29.804
That's bullshit.

13:32.599 --> 13:34.560
These woods are thick.

13:35.186 --> 13:36.437
You excited?

13:37.480 --> 13:38.398
You got it.

13:39.066 --> 13:42.070
I hope he's not shooting a
whole shitload of stock.

14:04.808 --> 14:06.602
I could help, but I'd
rather record.

14:06.811 --> 14:07.562
Okay.

14:07.854 --> 14:10.607
Packs on, we're ready to go.

14:10.774 --> 14:12.652
We gotta go up to the shack?

14:12.860 --> 14:13.611
Yeah.

14:20.412 --> 14:22.873
My God, this is a very heavy pack.

14:26.420 --> 14:28.380
Off to Coffin Rock.

14:28.547 --> 14:30.508
I know exactly where we are now.

14:31.551 --> 14:32.720
Mikey, give me the video camera.

14:32.928 --> 14:35.139
I wanna get her going across, man.

14:38.978 --> 14:40.939
I see a dirty behind.

14:45.111 --> 14:46.112
Good jump.

