at Coffin Rock.

16:01.878 --> 16:05.383
Let's rush, because I want
to camp, and it's 4:52.

16:05.591 --> 16:08.512
It's late. We're gonna be
losing light soon.

16:10.056 --> 16:13.393
But I can use the shot
without me in it...

16:13.769 --> 16:17.774
...because I recorded sound
while reading the whole thing,...

16:18.316 --> 16:20.528
...so I'm sure I can edit
it together somehow.

