16:26.994 --> 16:27.996
Did you rent this thing?

16:28.246 --> 16:31.918
Yeah. I don't have a
tent for three people.

16:32.418 --> 16:33.503
Just wondering...

16:33.753 --> 16:35.798
I don't usually travel with two men.

16:36.215 --> 16:39.803
