If it smells of farts
too much in the night...

16:51.026 --> 16:53.321
Okay, so I can't have a
cigarette in the tent,...

16:53.696 --> 16:55.740
...but he can fart as
much as he wants?

16:55.949 --> 16:59.621
No, I never gave Mike
a fart allowance.

17:00.455 --> 17:02.040
You heard noises last night?

17:02.166 --> 17:04.711
- I did.
- Problem is, I sleep like a log.

17:04.961 --> 17:07.339
There were two separate noises...

17:07.589 --> 17:10.468
...coming from two
areas over here...

17:11.303 --> 17:13.180
...one of them could
have been an owl...

17:13.388 --> 17:15.599
...but the other was a cackling.

17:16.935 --> 17:18.020
No way.

17:18.228 --> 17:19.814
It was a cackling, man.

17:20.064 --> 17:22.442
If I heard a cackling,
I would've shit myself.

17:23.068 --> 17:24.862
Where did we start yesterday?

17:25.154 --> 17:26.656
Off the map.

17:27.406 --> 17:31.245
I knew where we were going.
There was some confusion, but today...

17:31.454 --> 17:32.789
Wait,... say that again.

17:32.998 --> 17:35.209
I said I knew where
we were going.

17:35.459 --> 17:38.421
Wait,... was that a
full of shit statement?

17:38.588 --> 17:39.256
No, it wasn't.

17:39.464 --> 17:41.425
- So that wasn't bullshit?
- I knew where we were going.

17:41.592 --> 17:43.804
You got us lost, man.

17:43.970 --> 17:45.848
For a very short period of time.

17:46.390 --> 17:48.017
Just don't get us lost today.

17:48.184 --> 17:48.852
Yeah, seriously.

17:49.060 --> 17:50.854
No. These places are
very well documented.

17:51.063 --> 17:53.107
You happy with the documentary?

17:53.358 --> 17:54.276
Yes, I am.

17:55.277 --> 17:58.156
I'm very pleasantly surprised
by our little Mikey.

17:58.364 --> 17:59.449
"Our Little Mikey?"

17:59.783 --> 18:01.034
Our Little Mikey...

18:04.414 --> 18:05.999
...a very spirited young man.

18:06.500 --> 18:09.212
What do you think about the
witch? You think she exists?

18:09.587 --> 18:11.214
I don't know.

18:13.885 --> 18:16.179
Heather, I really hope
you find us a trail.

18:16.513 --> 18:19.350
There's a trail up on
this hill. Don't worry.

18:21.728 --> 18:23.606
We like shortcuts, don't we?

18:25.942 --> 18:28.070
We like level shortcuts.

18:28.904 --> 18:30.782
Not mountain shortcuts.

18:31.116 --> 18:33.577
It's the first time we've
seen Mike's chest.

18:33.744 --> 18:36.039
It's really hard to film on video.

18:36.539 --> 18:39.084
He has really sporadic hair
patterns on his chest.

18:39.251 --> 18:40.169
Like symbols.

18:40.336 --> 18:42.881
It's like blank... hairy...

18:43.257 --> 18:44.967
...blank... hairy.

18:45.176 --> 18:46.094
You should see my ass.

18:46.344 --> 18:48.138
Look, here's fucking Uruguay.

18:49.765 --> 18:51.476
- And there's Paraguay.
- Yeah.

18:51.768 --> 18:53.144
I think I see Bolivia.

18:53.353 --> 18:57.108
What killed this
mouse? Witchcraft?

18:59.486 --> 19:00.821
How 'bout God?

19:02.031 --> 19:03.658
Is that the Blair Witch?

19:04.075 --> 19:08.456
No. I think it's Heather,
taking a piss.

19:09.583 --> 19:12.670
You know, I
really have to go.

19:13.963 --> 19:15.382
Ohhh... go!

19:16.508 --> 19:20.013
We're near the cemetery
trail. It should only be...

19:20.305 --> 19:22.099
- What?
- Says who?

19:22.308 --> 19:23.309
Says me, of course.

19:24.477 --> 19:28.065
We should be there
in about ninety minutes.

19:30.402 --> 19:31.653
You guys cool with that?

19:32.488 --> 19:33.155
What?

19:33.322 --> 19:34.407
Ninety minutes?

19:34.699 --> 19:37.244
- If you know where we're going.
- Sure.

19:37.536 --> 19:39.413
Josh wants to look at the map now.

19:39.622 --> 19:41.500
Though I know
where we're going.

19:41.708 --> 19:44.003
If you'd known where
we were, we wouldn't be...

19:44.211 --> 19:45.296
We're in the middle
of the fucking woods.

19:45.421 --> 19:48.050
- How could you possibly know?
- Because some is offtrail.

19:48.217 --> 19:50.887
What, somebody told you
there's a cemetery back there?

19:51.095 --> 19:53.557
If we're lost, admit that, because...

19:53.807 --> 19:54.976
...I know we're not lost.

19:55.184 --> 19:57.479
You knew that yesterday, too,
and twice again today.

19:57.646 --> 20:00.650
Bullshit! We have
not been lost today.

20:01.442 --> 20:02.819
Not once.

20:03.111 --> 20:04.029
Okay, this is where we were.

20:04.238 --> 20:06.783
You said that it was
two miles away.

20:06.950 --> 20:08.911
Then it's two hours away,
three hours away...

20:09.119 --> 20:11.664
- Okay, just chill!
- Maybe it's four hours away.

20:11.831 --> 20:14.668
- You agreed to do this project.
- I agreed to a scouted-out project.

20:14.835 --> 20:17.672
- Not to wander round the woods.
- I told you that...

20:17.881 --> 20:20.259
...getting to the locations
wasn't gonna be easy.

20:20.509 --> 20:22.303
Mike, Mike... Okay, guys!

20:22.470 --> 20:24.681
Please, you're being a smart-ass.

20:24.890 --> 20:26.141
We're looking at the map...

20:26.350 --> 20:28.895
...we'll find this the best we can.

20:29.145 --> 20:32.900
This is where we were. We're
going more or less this way.

20:33.693 --> 20:36.363
Okay, what do you say? Where
do you think we're going?

20:37.072 --> 20:38.324
To tell you the truth...

20:42.580 --> 20:45.417
...this is Greek
to me. It's useless.

20:45.584 --> 20:46.418
Exactly.

20:46.668 --> 20:48.212
So I'm putting my trust in you...

20:48.379 --> 20:51.341
...that you know where it is.

20:52.176 --> 20:53.093
Good.

20:54.345 --> 20:56.890
Though I gotta tell you,
I don't fully trust you...

20:58.017 --> 20:59.018
...and I...

20:59.727 --> 21:00.728
What?

21:01.021 --> 21:03.899
I don't know why you tape
every conversation, man.

21:04.066 --> 21:05.151
Well, we're making a documentary.

21:05.401 --> 21:08.489
Not about us getting lost,
it's about a witch!

21:09.865 --> 21:11.242
I have a camera.

21:11.868 --> 21:15.790
We'll all look back on this
and laugh, believe me.

21:16.332 --> 21:18.293
Baby steps, man, baby steps.

21:18.502 --> 21:21.756
Just breathe and don't look down.
No, you gotta look down.

21:21.923 --> 21:23.341
Are you gonna have to crawl?

21:23.508 --> 21:24.092
I'm gonna crawl.

21:24.259 --> 21:24.843
Cool.

21:25.010 --> 21:28.598
Think how cool the fucking
cemetery is gonna be.

21:30.768 --> 21:33.563
Think of the joy of being
in a really good film.

21:33.772 --> 21:34.606
Okay, shut the fuck up.

21:34.773 --> 21:36.025
Okay, I'm quiet.

21:36.192 --> 21:37.360
Shit. How am I gonna do this?

21:37.568 --> 21:39.696
Okay... Mikey?

21:39.905 --> 21:40.489
Yeah.

21:40.781 --> 21:44.453
Dude, don't come across
with the DAT on your belly.

21:44.745 --> 21:45.579
No way, man.

21:45.788 --> 21:47.039
There's no chance.

21:47.498 --> 21:49.292
How do we get it
across?

21:49.459 --> 21:50.377
It's really fucking hard.

21:50.544 --> 21:51.795
How we gonna get
it across?

21:51.962 --> 21:55.300
The moss this morning was easy.
This stuff's slippery as shit.

21:56.218 --> 21:57.929
Well, how do we get
the DAT across?

21:59.431 --> 22:02.518
I don't know. Let
me put my pack down...

22:02.726 --> 22:04.437
I'll just go back and forth, man.

22:04.646 --> 22:06.690
Can you do it that way?

22:06.940 --> 22:08.359
It's the only thing I can do.

22:08.567 --> 22:09.986
Okay, we'll do it like that.

22:10.195 --> 22:11.279
Oh, Christ!

22:11.488 --> 22:13.365
Oh, what'd you drop?

22:13.616 --> 22:17.371
Nothing.
The tree just broke.

22:17.579 --> 22:18.664
Oh, fuck.

22:18.873 --> 22:20.917
We're very, very close now.

22:23.545 --> 22:25.089
You guys excited?

22:27.884 --> 22:29.261
Okay.

22:29.929 --> 22:31.306
What's this?

22:38.815 --> 22:41.569
What's this? Dude, guys.

22:43.280 --> 22:45.825
Remember what Mary
Brown said the other day?

22:47.577 --> 22:50.289
What story from the
Bible was she telling us?

22:50.497 --> 22:52.792
Fuck, I wasn't listening, I
thought she was crazy.

22:53.335 --> 22:56.213
It was Esau, something about a
pile of rocks.

22:56.923 --> 22:59.551
She was talking
about her rocks, man.

22:59.801 --> 23:01.929
Well, what about
the rocks?

23:03.389 --> 23:05.183
Anybody remember?

23:06.435 --> 23:09.856
To live your life.

23:11.191 --> 23:13.486
Looks like an Indian
burial ground, man.

23:13.736 --> 23:15.697
I don't know if this counts,
three...

23:17.783 --> 23:18.701
...four...

23:21.246 --> 23:22.164
...five...

23:23.249 --> 23:24.250
...six...

23:25.710 --> 23:26.628
...seven.

23:26.879 --> 23:28.589
Years ago witches
were roasted...

23:28.798 --> 23:30.842
...just like my Vienna sausage.

23:31.468 --> 23:34.347
Flames are licking you
like the Devil, Josh.

23:34.555 --> 23:37.976
Sit back and hear a tale,
a tale of a fateful trip...

23:38.268 --> 23:40.480
...that started on
this desert isle...

23:40.688 --> 23:42.566
...aboard this tiny ship...

23:42.733 --> 23:44.860
Yeah, but this ship
has a good captain...

23:45.027 --> 23:47.405
...not a beer-guzzling
guy in a blue shirt.

23:47.739 --> 23:49.241
He wasn't beer-guzzling.

23:49.784 --> 23:51.828
They had no beer on
the island, man.

23:52.037 --> 23:54.999
If they had beer, they'd
have had big-ass orgies.

23:56.417 --> 23:59.588
You're like the Captain,
and Mike's your Gilligan.

24:00.089 --> 24:01.632
- No offense.
- That's all right.

24:01.925 --> 24:03.260
It was a compliment...

24:04.845 --> 24:06.347
...Gilligan was a funny guy...

24:06.639 --> 24:08.767
...the Captain was fat, though.

24:08.934 --> 24:11.228
Well okay, let's call
it a thin Captain.

24:11.479 --> 24:12.981
It's not Captain...

24:13.189 --> 24:15.651
It's the Skipper.

24:17.361 --> 24:18.530
No more Captain.

24:20.491 --> 24:23.161
Here we are back at
the rock again...

24:23.328 --> 24:25.038
...the cemetery deal.

24:26.832 --> 24:28.960
I just wanna be careful
not to get in the shot.

24:37.596 --> 24:39.223
It certainly is odd.

24:45.732 --> 24:48.652
Please tell me you didn't
just knock that over.

24:48.903 --> 24:50.447
I didn't just knock that over.

24:50.655 --> 24:54.702
That's not very nice.
Let me put it back.

25:03.046 --> 25:04.757
You can't be too careful.

25:05.174 --> 25:06.551
What'd you think?

25:07.594 --> 25:10.848
It was the same, only darker.

25:11.474 --> 25:13.101
Yeah, pretty much.

25:14.353 --> 25:16.898
All right. Bag it up.

25:17.691 --> 25:18.692
Hello?

25:20.236 --> 25:21.863
Shit, no light.

25:28.622 --> 25:30.207
We were sleeping.

25:30.416 --> 25:31.333
Do you want this?

25:32.460 --> 25:34.337
Put it by the tent door.

25:48.314 --> 25:49.482
Listen.

25:51.109 --> 25:52.111
Hello?

25:53.821 --> 25:54.823
Hello!

26:02.499 --> 26:06.087
It's all around us.
Fucking weird.

26:06.755 --> 26:08.632
Michael, aren't you
coming down?

26:09.050 --> 26:10.134
I ain't going down there.

26:10.426 --> 26:11.595
Why not?

26:11.803 --> 26:13.514
- Because I don't hear shit.
- You're fucking scared.

26:13.681 --> 26:14.849
Because I don't
hear anything!

26:15.057 --> 26:17.269
You cannot deny hearing it.

26:18.312 --> 26:20.189
Get your ass out! Come on!

26:22.567 --> 26:24.612
This rain fucking blows, man.

26:24.862 --> 26:26.823
I know. It's raining heavily.

26:27.449 --> 26:30.953
Thanks mom for giving me
rain gear for my birthday.

26:31.204 --> 26:32.789
God bless her.

26:33.039 --> 26:35.000
What do you think it
was last night?

26:36.377 --> 26:37.879
Personally?

26:38.004 --> 26:38.588
Yeah.

26:38.755 --> 26:40.966
Someone fucking
with your head.

26:41.175 --> 26:42.969
But nobody knows
we're here.

26:43.178 --> 26:45.639
Yeah, but... you ever see
"Deliverance"?

26:46.140 --> 26:49.645
Well, whatever it was,
I just wanted to...

26:49.811 --> 26:52.023
You were freaking out.
You bugged me out.

26:52.231 --> 26:55.235
I was. I woke up suddenly
and shit's going down...

26:55.402 --> 26:57.029
...and all I can think is
"I want it all...

26:57.238 --> 26:59.950
I want it on sound,
I want it on sixteen.

27:00.117 --> 27:02.870
If we see anything,
I want it on sixteen. "

27:03.329 --> 27:06.417
Sounded to me like a lot
of people running around...

27:06.625 --> 27:08.586
...maybe they were locals
or whatever.

27:08.753 --> 27:10.714
I don't know what
the hell they wanted.

27:10.922 --> 27:14.969
We're deep in the woods, and
if people want to mess with us...

27:15.136 --> 27:17.181
...then there's something
wrong with them...

27:17.389 --> 27:18.808
...and I'm not gonna
get into that.

27:18.975 --> 27:20.143
And if it wasn't people?

27:20.351 --> 27:22.229
Well, I'm not gonna
get into that, either!

27:23.814 --> 27:24.816
Fuck, man...

27:26.818 --> 27:28.612
... it's been a very long day...

27:28.779 --> 27:31.616
...a very wet, very long day.

27:34.620 --> 27:38.041
Nobody's speaking to me
right now.

27:38.625 --> 27:41.254
Dude, I don't remember
any of this.

27:42.130 --> 27:43.298
What?

27:43.465 --> 27:46.219
I don't remember any
of this coming from the car.

27:46.386 --> 27:50.224
We have to go a different
route to get back...

27:50.474 --> 27:52.519
...because we went
around in a curve.

27:54.980 --> 27:57.191
Two more hours max, guys.

27:59.278 --> 28:03.199
If we came by a short cut, why
are we going back a different way?

28:04.993 --> 28:07.038
Because we have to go round...

28:07.664 --> 28:10.125
It was the most direct way to
hit our two locations.

28:10.584 --> 28:12.295
And this is the quickest
way back to the car.

28:12.503 --> 28:13.421
Seriously?

28:13.630 --> 28:15.048
Yes. Seriously.

28:15.215 --> 28:18.094
- You know exactly what's going on?
- Yes. Let's just keep going.

28:18.302 --> 28:19.387
All right.

28:20.263 --> 28:22.558
Five minutes and we
do a map check.

28:23.017 --> 28:24.102
All right.

28:24.853 --> 28:28.691
We just did a map check,
and we're still on track.

28:29.526 --> 28:31.028
That's not what I said.

28:31.862 --> 28:34.157
We're all right. Come on,
just keep going.

28:37.745 --> 28:39.872
Well the compass says...

28:40.123 --> 28:42.334
...we go straight ahead,
that way.

28:43.043 --> 28:45.171
We're in the middle of nowhere.

28:45.547 --> 28:48.092
We've been in the middle
of nowhere for two days.

28:48.258 --> 28:49.969
Just like the car.

28:50.136 --> 28:52.806
Look at this shit, man!
This is nothing.

28:54.266 --> 28:56.227
Let's just keep
going, all right?

28:59.231 --> 29:00.691
I think we should camp.

29:00.858 --> 29:01.943
Get the fuck out of here!

29:02.152 --> 29:04.196
Why? 'Cause you don't know
where we are?

29:04.363 --> 29:06.407
No, because we're still
A little way from the car...

29:06.616 --> 29:07.951
...and it's gonna be dark soon.

29:09.369 --> 29:12.707
- Look, I'm not sure...
- We don't camp. Stop the camera...

29:12.874 --> 29:13.959
...and get us home.

29:14.126 --> 29:17.547
Turn the camera off and give
me the fucking map.

29:17.797 --> 29:19.216
Turn it off and get us home.

29:19.383 --> 29:22.553
No, I'm filming. I want
to mark this occasion.

29:22.762 --> 29:23.763
Give me the map.

29:23.972 --> 29:26.892
The map is in my
pocket. Wait a second.

29:27.059 --> 29:28.311
God damn!

29:28.770 --> 29:32.108
If we keep our heads
together, we'll be just fine.

29:32.275 --> 29:33.776
Fucking bullshit!

29:33.943 --> 29:35.028
Mike, chill.

29:35.529 --> 29:36.780
Just relax, Mike.

29:37.031 --> 29:39.075
Don't fucking tell
me to relax!

29:39.617 --> 29:42.705
Let's just sit down,
and check the map...

29:42.872 --> 29:44.916
Yes. Let's do that, please.

29:46.293 --> 29:47.628
Are you happy?

29:47.795 --> 29:49.172
I'm not happy, no.

29:49.964 --> 29:52.968
But the car isn't far. But we
can't find it in the dark.

29:53.177 --> 29:55.931
Are you absolutely sure?

29:56.139 --> 29:59.978
Yes. I'm so sorry. We can still
get the DAT back tomorrow.

30:00.103 --> 30:01.354
We have to...

30:01.563 --> 30:04.901
We will get the
DAT back on time.

30:05.109 --> 30:06.528
And the camera.

30:06.695 --> 30:08.155
We'll get it all
back tomorrow.

30:08.322 --> 30:10.700
I start work tomorrow at nine.

30:10.909 --> 30:11.910
I know.

30:12.077 --> 30:14.121
It's fine. Let's go to sleep.

30:14.288 --> 30:16.416
Let's just fucking camp, okay?

30:16.875 --> 30:19.002
I wanna tape it from
inside the tent.

30:24.802 --> 30:27.764
Whatever it is, it sounds the
same as last night.

30:35.190 --> 30:38.027
Where's my boots? Fuck, it's cold...

30:42.992 --> 30:43.910
Hello?

30:47.915 --> 30:50.752
Shit, it's fucking freezing...

30:51.962 --> 30:52.964
...there.

30:54.174 --> 30:55.091
What?

30:55.300 --> 30:56.385
I hear it.

30:57.011 --> 30:58.429
I don't hear shit.

30:59.514 --> 31:00.891
You hear that?

31:07.149 --> 31:08.067
Shit...

31:18.455 --> 31:19.540
Hello?

31:49.371 --> 31:51.582
I think it's just a deer.

31:52.625 --> 31:55.170
- Could be deer, I guess.
- It's just a deer.

31:55.421 --> 31:56.964
I don't think so, man.

31:57.089 --> 32:00.260
Sounds just like last night.
It's all around us.

32:00.469 --> 32:01.721
It's gotta be just a deer.

32:01.929 --> 32:03.306
It was a deer, man.

32:04.349 --> 32:05.893
It wasn't like last night.

32:12.151 --> 32:13.069
You say something?

32:13.236 --> 32:16.824
Yes! Fucking listen! Let's
get it on DAT... be quiet...

32:17.032 --> 32:18.451
Okay, it's on.

32:22.206 --> 32:24.959
Jesus Christ! What the
fuck was that?

32:32.010 --> 32:34.055
It's not scared by our yelling.

32:39.103 --> 32:40.814
Sounds like footsteps.

32:41.022 --> 32:43.066
I know! It's a fucking person!

32:44.735 --> 32:47.906
I don't see shit on video.
We'll just use DAT, right?

32:48.115 --> 32:48.949
But I'm staying out.

32:49.116 --> 32:50.493
You stay out here with me.

32:50.660 --> 32:51.745
I am. I am.

32:52.078 --> 32:56.000
What time is it? Anywhere
near morning?

32:56.960 --> 32:57.627
Let me see...

32:57.836 --> 33:00.381
Tell me it's five
O'clock or something.

33:01.883 --> 33:02.634
Three.

33:02.801 --> 33:03.635
Fuck!

33:05.137 --> 33:08.308
Bullshit. This is
fucking crazy.

33:10.185 --> 33:12.730
I'm sorry, Mike. We should
be home already.

33:12.939 --> 33:14.983
This has got nothing to do...

33:16.068 --> 33:17.862
...with what we're here for.

33:18.071 --> 33:19.948
This is just it's bullshit.

33:20.908 --> 33:23.870
Woke up this morning,
two seconds ago...

33:24.538 --> 33:27.208
...and there are piles of
rocks outside our tent.

33:31.046 --> 33:32.840
There are three, actually.

33:34.509 --> 33:37.471
Are you positive those
weren't there last night?

33:37.680 --> 33:40.559
I am fucking positive
they weren't here!

33:40.809 --> 33:43.187
How could we have
just camped...

33:43.354 --> 33:46.692
...between three piles of rocks
just by coincidence?

33:47.484 --> 33:49.111
You don't think this is strange?

33:49.696 --> 33:53.200
It is fucking weird, but
I really don't care...

33:53.409 --> 33:55.954
...because all I want to do
is get to the goddam car.

33:56.162 --> 33:59.250
